ECHØVEIL RECORDS.about:
ECHØVEIL RADIO // VOLUME III — WITH SPECTRE HORSEMEN, PALE WITH DUST !!!!
Behold, wandering listeners of the brume-saturated night… Volume III of ECHØVEIL’s Radiophonic Experiment slithers out of its chrysalis of static and delirium, dripping with iridescent spores and questionable benevolence. Sir Kuliktavikt, still possessed by seventeen incompatible dream-spirits and one extremely confused radio antenna, returns to feed your trembling ears a banquet of styles stitched together with occult dental floss.
Tonight, the frequencies buckle and bloom:
ghostly psych-dream folk whispering in your fourth eyelid;
minimalist ambient noise wall chiselling slow cosmic graffiti on your skull;
free-spiritual jazz spiralling up into dimensions only recently legalized;
black ambient gnawing the enamel of your sanity;
old-school drone floating like a dead saint in colloidal light;
dizzying avant-prog pirouetting on a broken tibia;
experimental rock exhaling fungal riddles;
piano notes desolate enough to make angels cough;
Ethiopian jazz-funk shimmering like a ghost discothèque under the bed;
frozen dungeon synth shivering in chainmail reverie;
and yes — a microscopic, rebellious wink of calypso, because even nightmares need a sunburn.
And descending through the vapour, our honored guest materializes: Spectre Horsemen, Pale With Dust — an experimental sonic entity first spotted in October 2023. His sound merges dark ambient, post-industrial murmurs, doom-jazz exhales, drone incantations, power-electronics ruptures, and noise mutations… recombined into a haunted architecture that feels like a cathedral built inside an abandoned ribcage. Truly singular. Truly nightmarish. Truly wonderful.
If you dare, wander through his lair:
spectrehorsemenpalewithdust.bandcamp.com
Tune in, tune out, tune sideways — the radio is alive, and it’s hungry.
